    "description": "使學生瞭解資訊系統的基本架構、UI設計的實例與原則交互驗證、理解物理性與軟體制約原理、介面的方向性原則與互動方法介紹、無縫式介面設計方法介紹、UX經驗設計的準則說明<br>",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1. 立體構造與佈局模式：瞭解資訊系統的基本架構<br>2. 導覽列與一致性：ＵＩ設計的實例與原則交互驗證<br>3. 物理性與軟體制約：理解物理性與軟體制約原理<br>4. 捲動的方向性與裝置互動：介面的方向性原則與互動方法介紹<br>5. 無縫式介面：無縫式介面設計方法介紹<br>6. 經驗設計：ＵＸ經驗設計的準則說明<br>",
        "en": "1. Stereoscopic structure and layout mode: understanding the basic structure of the<br>information system<br>2. Navigation and consistency: UI verification examples and principles of interactive<br>verification<br>3. Physical and soft systems: understanding the principles of physical and soft<br>systems <br>4. The directionality of scrolling and device interaction: the orientation<br>principle and interaction method of interface<br>5. Seamless interface: introduction to seamless interface design method <br>6. Experience Design: Guidelines for UX Experience Design"
